;                           Name of the attribute that is a substitute for 'SCALEMIN'.
;       SCALEMAX:           in, optional, type=string
;                           Name of the attribute that is a substitute for 'SCALEMAX'.
;-
pro MrCDF_Viewer::SetConfig, $
